<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267882>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Chaetostoma joropo n. sp., coloration in life from the río Güejar, Meta, Colombia. Specimens not preserved. Photographs by O. Lucanus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267882/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267883>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ontogenetic variation in color pattern in Chaetostoma joropo n. sp. (left, MPUJ 7199) and Chaetostoma milesi (right, CZUT-IC 10593). Juveniles below, subadults in middle row, adults above. Scale bar equals 1 cm. Photographs by A. Urbano-Bonilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267884>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distribution map of Chaetostoma joropo n. sp. (triangles) and Chaetostoma milesi (circles) in cis- and trans- Andean Colombia, respectively. Type localities are indicated by numbers for both C. joropo (1) and C. milesi (2)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267885>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitat of Chaetostoma joropo n. sp. in the Serranía de La Macarena. Photograph by A. Urbano-Bonilla." ;
